diff -ruN /mnt/data/oplsrc/Open-PS2-Loader-latest/PATCH_1080P_BOOT_NOTES.txt /mnt/data/opl_boot1080_src/PATCH_1080P_BOOT_NOTES.txt
--- /mnt/data/oplsrc/Open-PS2-Loader-latest/PATCH_1080P_BOOT_NOTES.txt	1970-01-01 00:00:00.000000000 +0000
+++ /mnt/data/opl_boot1080_src/PATCH_1080P_BOOT_NOTES.txt	2026-05-09 21:03:26.386452868 +0000
@@ -0,0 +1,16 @@
+Patch aplicado no OPL 2241/39afed2:
+
+- NAO altera a tela/interface HIRES do OPL.
+- NAO substitui 720p nem 1080i originais.
+- Adiciona 2 opcoes extras no final da lista GSM:
+  1) HDTV 1080p @60Hz LISO BOOT TESTE
+  2) HDTV 1080p @60Hz LISO BOOT SAFE
+
+Base tecnica:
+- GS_MODE_DTV_1080P = 0x54
+- GS_NONINTERLACED
+- GS_FRAME
+- DISPLAY 1920x1080
+
+Se der sem sinal ao iniciar jogo, volte para GSM OFF ou HDTV 720p @60Hz.
+Nem todo jogo/TV/conversor aceita 1080p forçado.
diff -ruN /mnt/data/oplsrc/Open-PS2-Loader-latest/include/renderman.h /mnt/data/opl_boot1080_src/include/renderman.h
--- /mnt/data/oplsrc/Open-PS2-Loader-latest/include/renderman.h	2026-04-09 21:17:14.000000000 +0000
+++ /mnt/data/opl_boot1080_src/include/renderman.h	2026-05-09 21:03:26.381512212 +0000
@@ -17,6 +17,10 @@
 /// DTV 576 Progressive Scan (720x576). Not available in ROM v1.70 and earlier.
 #define GS_MODE_DTV_576P 0x53
 
+/// DTV 1080 Progressive Scan (1920x1080). Experimental GSM mode.
+/// Some TVs/capture devices reject 1080p from PS2/component/HDMI converters.
+#define GS_MODE_DTV_1080P 0x54
+
 #define DIM_UNDEF -1
 
 #define ALIGN_TOP     (0 << 0)
